  <brief_title>Mindfulness-based Stress Reduction (MBSR) Program Combined With Endurance Exercise Training: a Help in Treatment for Breast Cancer?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Mindfulness-based Stress Reduction (MBSR) Program Combined With Endurance Exercise Training: a Help to Improve Exercise Capacity and Quality of Life in Breast Cancer?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
